YTQyYWJkMTJhIiwibGlua19pZCI6MTAzNzUyOX0/6aea19836e1577cef67eef91d93fc4e3ea8=
bb132ca0207f18609784913bf14eb" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-decoration:none;=
font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">newly released financial report</a></u>,
the company has struggled, losing about $1 million in 2023=E2=80=94a revers=
al from a small net profit the year before=E2=80=94due in part to declining=
 revenue in its auction and private sales business. Also buried within the =
report, Artnet revealed it took loans totaling approximately $2 million fro=
m a third party, a senior executive, and the former C.E.O., presumably to c=
over operating losses.  <br/><br/>On one level, Artnet held its own amid a =
downturn, only losing 4 percent of the previous year=E2=80=99s topline reve=
nue. =E2=80=9C2023 was a difficult year for us and the entire art market,=
=E2=80=9D C.E.O. <b>Jacob</b> <b>Pabst</b> wrote in a letter accompanying t=
he financial report. =E2=80=9CAs a result, sales at the major auction house=
s plummeted, as did our own.=E2=80=9D Pabst also previewed a significant re=
structuring program. =E2=80=9CThe cost reduction measures have already beco=
me evident in 2023, with savings of over 1.5 million USD,=E2=80=9D he wrote=
, =E2=80=9Cto which an additional 3.5 million USD will be added this year.
In 2025, these measures will then fully take effect, resulting in savings o=
f nearly 6 million USD.=E2=80=9D For a company that does around $25 million=
 in revenue, cost savings of that magnitude would be a real achievement. <b=
r/><br/>Alas, this financial engineering may be necessary to stave off a le=
adership change at the publicly traded firm. The value of Artnet=E2=80=99s =
brand, as I tried to <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9p=
ZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dTQXVsbTE4aUJHUy14UzdpYUJBMD0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR=
0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5ld3MvY291bGQtYXJ0bmV0LWZvdW5kZXItYmUtZm9yY2VkLW91dC8_dXRtX2=
NhbXBhaWduPVdhbGwrUG93ZXIrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjg5JTJGMTclMkYyNCUyOVx1MDAyN=
nV0bV9jb250ZW50PVdhbGwrUG93ZXIrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjg5JTJGMSUyRjI0JTI5XHUw=
MDI2dXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbF9hY3Rpb25cdTAwMjZ1dG1fc291cmNlPWN1c3RvbWVyLmlvXHU=
wMDI2dXRtX3Rlcm09ZjZjNjA2MTdkYTQyYWJkMTJhIiwiaW50ZXJuYWwiOiJmNmM2MDYxN2RhND=
